Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:04.68,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As times change,\Ndifficult cases increase in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:08.59,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's case involves three siblings!\NMysteries upon mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:10.49,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:12.96,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:15.55,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.32,0:01:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh! And I came all this way because he said it was a big incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should've just taken the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! I'm not gonna search for some lousy missing iguana!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:55.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sounds perfect for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What seems to be the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.21,0:02:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My car broke down on me. Could I ask for a lift to my villa up ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll compensate you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd be glad to give you a lift!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you. My name is Hotta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.33,0:02:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:24.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kosaku Hotta, Pres. Of Hotta Industries
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hotta Industries!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:28.44,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hotta Industries â€”\hPresident\NKosaku Hotta (58)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:28.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You run that huge corporation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yamauchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My car broke down. These folks gave me a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:02.93,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Villa Caretaker\NMasahiro Yamauchi (55)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so? I'm Yamauchi, the caretaker of this villa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:09.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing! I'm sure he would've done the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:12.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are Koichi and the others already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Everyone is worried because you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder. I bet they hope I died in an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.73,0:03:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Tonight is my birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to invite you, as thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mind, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't arrive on time, Father, so we were worried
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:51.35,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Eldest Son\NKoichi Hotta (39)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you had gotten in an accident along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Hotta Industries is nothing without you, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:55.52,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Koichi's Wife\NHarumi Hotta (36)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:04:00.24,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Second Son\NRyoji Hotta (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:04:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For sure! The company needs you to stay well for a long time to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chateau Petrus, 1979. From Koichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. Is that expensive wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Eye-poppingly expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the king of red wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, let us toast to Father's 58th birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you drink first, big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:46.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just figured it wouldn't be funny if there was poison in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How rude, Ryoji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:05:01.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The overseas branch has taken big hits because of your poor forecasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I hear you're going to be dismissed and sent to a subsidiary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're suggesting I'm planning to kill Father over that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear you've racked up some heavy-duty gambling debts lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've had just about enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:32.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see my brothers are as close as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:35.71,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Eldest Daughter\NFumiko Hotta (30)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:34.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a harsh hello, after sending an invitation yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We severed all ties five years ago! I'd never send you an invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see your face! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who called me here to tell me something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to say to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight was supposed to be a feast, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:05.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what happened between Hotta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:14.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good question. I've only been their caretaker for two years,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I don't know what happened long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:31.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whiskey, huh? Whose present is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-W-What theâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What theâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I can assume a bomb was planted in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:01.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:05.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay out! Please wait outside until the police arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:09.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The world's greatest detective, Kogoro Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.19,0:07:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogoro Mouri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The famous detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was dynamite...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't smell like dynamite to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trying to butt in again, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He has wood and glass fragments in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid kid! Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:41.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is a whiskey display box!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:46.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah! The glass stuck in him is from a bottle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomb was inside the whiskey box!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why there are fragments all over Hotta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I seeâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:08:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't need you to tell me! I realized that long before you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:10.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Dirt? What's it doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Yamauchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:17.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says the phone is out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anyone here holds a grudge against Father... it's you, Fumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You hadn't spoken in five years!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suddenly showing up now without an invitation is undeniably strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I did hate him. Enough to want to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I didn't do it. Though I do thank whoever did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I assume you all feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What horrible siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are the phone lines?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've been cut by a knife or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A knife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomb was planted inside a whiskey box.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? T-This display box wasâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You recognize it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it was a present Ryoji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r} gave to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember because I took it to his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Ryoji did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, where is Ryoji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He ran off...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Ryoji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}'s car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:10:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hasn't gotten far, if he left his car behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Does that mean he's still lurking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:11.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's this?! It's been slashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably best to leave in our cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All four of these cars have slashed tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Does that mean we can't leave this villa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryoji did this. There's rubber stuck on his knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't drive, so we took a limo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there any other cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's my car. But it's broken and hardly in a usable state...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, if Ryoji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the killer, why would he slash his own tires?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? If his tires were the only ones not slashed,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:11:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the police would suspect him right off the bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:05.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange. He would still be suspected right off the bat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:10.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}if his whiskey exploded and he disappeared right after!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:13.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ryoji{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} didn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:17.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But if the killer's goal was actually to trap everyone inside this villa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:20.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...something else might happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any event, Ryoji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is still lurking around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure to stay together and not go off alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.21,0:11:30.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Screw that! I'm going back to my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, right after I warn her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us all go back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. I'll try to fix my car...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be extremely careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s pendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quiet! I'm busy right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you looking for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, little boy. This is the most important thing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that your lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died, five years ago. Suicideâ€”\Nno, it was more like murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By Hotta Kosaku, my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:50.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I left. I couldn't forgive my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.23,0:12:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. I guess there's no point in telling this to a little kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:05.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} held a grudge against Hotta{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:11.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But did she have a chance to plant the bomb in the whiskey box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:18.63,Signs,,0,0,0,,Chemical Fertilizer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.12,0:13:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chemical fertilizer! Could that bomb have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:31.14,Signs,,0,0,0,,Sulfur
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:31.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sulfur and chemicals! And that chemical fertilizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No doubt about it! That person is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This person isâ€”!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:51.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:54.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Oh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That car sure is old!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the first one I ever designed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were a car designer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, until five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I quit after something happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a car like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's an old-style car, but it has an airbag...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, could you go get Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:28.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To get the police. Everyone feels uneasy with just Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the caretaker. I have a responsibility to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.64,0:14:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, time for food!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably off playing somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:52.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a lost cause. I'll go find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My food...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:15:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be shocked. This photograph was in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went into my room without permission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found something interesting in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sulfur and other chemicals, hidden inside a cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The explosive wasn't dynamite. It was a homemade bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,made of chemical fertilizer, sulfur, and other chemicals!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can make a bomb out of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:35.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If mixed properly, it can produce an explosive as powerful as dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous! Why would I want to kill the master of the house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This incident was entirely to avenge the person in that photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hotta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} drove him to suicide five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was your son, Yamauchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Eh?!\N- Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were the one who took Ryoji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s whiskey
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and delivered it to Hotta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when you placed the homemade explosive inside the box,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,an igniter under the lid,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and easily-ignited phosphorus in the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was basically like striking a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't meant to be a perfect crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you needed to distance yourself from suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,until your next crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His next crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.42,0:16:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:46.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well done, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. It is just as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My son Kentaro was an extraordinary pianist with a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:17:00.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had dated a girl for a long time, but because of his paltry income,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:03.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he was unable to propose to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But five years ago, he won a competition and finally earned appraisal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then Kentaro proposed to her. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...the woman's fatherâ€”Hotta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}â€”was against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So that woman was Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kentaro met with Hotta to get permission to marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.21,0:17:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Hotta not only refused, but he ruined Kentaro's fingers as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The piano was Kentaro's life!\NAnd he had it stolen away forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, the woman ran off, leaving him behind devastated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the poor boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Upon learning all of this after his funeral, I was shocked to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that as a company man, I had known nothing about my own son...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.22,0:18:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's why you decided to get revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. After quitting the company, I investigated Hotta
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and became his caretaker to find a chance to exact revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:37.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Fumiko had left the family, and it took me two years to locate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you chose Hotta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s birthday party as the stage for revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:46.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and sent Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} an invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Now I will have no regrets in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is safe and sound in the carâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:19:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The moment I got her to step into that car, my revenge succeeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a trap in the car, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The airbag is set to go off when she steps hard on the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we speak, she's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really don't know anything, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you think Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is still single, after all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because even now, she continues to love Kentaro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:38.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absurd! A rude woman disowned by her father would never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wasn't disowned! She left on her own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She couldn't forgive her father for what he did to Kentaro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a lie! It's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She abandoned Kentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.95,0:19:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A treasure chest filled with her memories with Kentaro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and her feelings for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} always wears it at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even now, Kentaro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the dearest person to her, Yamauchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:27.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've killed the person who loved my son that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.50,0:20:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Didn't the airbag deploy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:54.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} tell me to come back right away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.14,0:20:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fumiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}... I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:03.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hated my father, too. Enough to want to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can't forgive Kentaro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He left me all alone... And drove his own father to do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really is sinful...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:12.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ryoji{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10} had been locked up in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:19.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.94,0:23:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Where did everyone go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.61,0:23:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm hungry. Oh, that's right! We're about to have breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamauchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Breakfast, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry I could die! Anything'll do, just please hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamauchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:57.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's strange! Something isn't right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:23:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.62,0:23:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to wash makeup off before applying a face pack!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:08.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-That's it! That person really is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.45,0:24:14.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-N-N-N-N-N-Next Conan's Hint: Lipstick
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.98,0:24:21.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time is an amazingly unique case!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:23.08,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Am I pretty?
